After over 90 years in the valley Dr.Mechanic has learned a few things about Preventative Maintenance. In most cases mechanical or electrical failures can be directly related to the lack of maintenance on your vehicle. Manufactures Recommended Maintenance schedules vary significantly. Dr.Mechanic Service Centers have the most current applications to make sure the factory maintenance records are completed to suffice even the strictest of warranties. With knowledgeable ASE Certified Master technicians and state of the art equipment, Dr.Mechanic has the expertise to give you peace of mind during services. Below is a list of vital preventative maintenance items to keep your vehicle running smooth: Oil, Lube, and Filter Transmission Service Fuel Injection Induction/Decarburization Service Ignition System Power Steering Flush Brake Fluid Flush Air Induction Service Coolant Flush Differential Service The above services should be performed regularly to maintain proper function and help avoid costly repairs. With locations all throughout the Valley there is bound to be a Dr.Mechanic Service Center near you. Call your nearest location to set up your vehicle Factory Scheduled Maintenance Service. All Wilhelm Service Centers offer a 36 month/36,000 mile warranty on all maintenance and repairs.w
